### Backend API Tests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or IntelliJ
### Copy this file to api-tests.http and update the values

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8531
@category = enemy

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get all entities
GET {{baseUrl}}/entities

### Get entities by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/entities?category={{category}}

### Initialize entities from storage
### Note: Update the path to your enemies-init.json file
POST {{baseUrl}}/entities/init
Content-Type: application/json

< ../../data/enemies-init.json

### Approve an image
POST {{baseUrl}}/images/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entityId": "ancient-robot",
  "model": "flux",
  "version": 1
}

### Deselect an image
POST {{baseUrl}}/images/deselect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entityId": "ancient-robot"
}
